# Pre-push parity gate. Runs the same checks GitHub Actions runs so CI
# failures get caught locally before they hit origin. Skips the slow
# `pnpm build` + Playwright steps — those stay in CI but are unlikely to
# fail if typecheck + lint + unit tests all pass.
#
# To bypass in an emergency: `git push --no-verify` (use sparingly; the
# whole point is that we *don't* push something CI will reject).

pnpm pre-push
